Exploratory data analysis

basic_eda <- function(data)
{
  glimpse(data)
  print(status(data))
  freq(data) 
  print(profiling_num(data))
  plot_num(data)
  #describe(data)
}

Modeling Bayes

Gaussian model

Prior predictive check

```r
m2 <- 
  brm( family = gaussian,                                                                       
       movie_overall_rating ~ 0 + condition,                                                           
       prior = c( prior( normal( 5, 0.5 ), class = b ),                      
                  prior( exponential( 1 ), class = sigma )),                                    
       sample_prior = \only\,
       data = df,
       iter = 2000, warmup = 1000, chains = 4, cores = 4
     )

```r
```r
m2b <- 
  brm( family = gaussian,                                                                       
       movie_overall_rating ~ 0 + condition,                                                           
       prior = c( prior( normal( 5, 0.5 ), class = b ),                      
                  prior( exponential( 1 ), class = sigma )),                                    
       # sample_prior = \only\,
       data = df,
       iter = 2000, warmup = 1000, chains = 4, cores = 4
     )

# Prior predictive check
pp_check( m2b ) + theme_bw()

## Ordinal model

Prior predictive check


<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuYGBgclxubTQgPC0gYnJtKCBmYW1pbHkgPSBjdW11bGF0aXZlLFxuICAgICAgICAgICBmb3JtdWxhID0gbW92aWVfb3ZlcmFsbF9yYXRpbmcgfiBjb25kaXRpb24sXG4gICAgICAgICAgIHByaW9yID0gYyhwcmlvcihub3JtYWwoMCwgMS41KSwgY2xhc3MgPSBJbnRlcmNlcHQpLFxuICAgICAgICAgICBwcmlvcihub3JtYWwoMCwgMC41KSwgY2xhc3MgPSBiKSksXG4gICAgICAgICAgIHNhbXBsZV9wcmlvciA9IFxcb25seVxcLFxuICAgICAgICAgICBkYXRhID0gZGYsIFxuICAgICAgICAgICBpdGVyID0gMjAwMCwgd2FybXVwID0gMTAwMCwgY29yZXMgPSA0LCBjaGFpbnMgPSA0IClcblxuIyBQcmlvciBwcmVkaWN0aXZlIGNoZWNrXG5wcF9jaGVjayggbTQgKSArIHRoZW1lX2J3KClcbmBgYFxuYGBgIn0= -->

```r
```r
m4 <- brm( family = cumulative,
           formula = movie_overall_rating ~ condition,
           prior = c(prior(normal(0, 1.5), class = Intercept),
           prior(normal(0, 0.5), class = b)),
           sample_prior = \only\,
           data = df, 
           iter = 2000, warmup = 1000, cores = 4, chains = 4 )

# Prior predictive check
pp_check( m4 ) + theme_bw()

```r
```r
m4b <- brm( family = cumulative,
            formula = movie_overall_rating ~ condition,
            prior = c(prior(normal(0, 1.5), class = Intercept), 
                      prior(normal(0, 0.5), class = b)),
            # sample_prior = \only\,
            data = df, 
            iter = 2000, warmup = 1000, cores = 4, chains = 4 )

# Prior predictive check
pp_check( m4b ) + theme_bw()

mcmc_areas(
    m4b,
    pars = c( \b_conditionprimacy\, \b_conditionrecency\),
    # regex_pars = \b_\,
    prob = 0.95,
    point_est = \median\,
    area_method = \equal area\
    ) +
    theme_bw()
